source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/tortelloni-with-peas-bacon-65254c40ca6ba9ab41630380
course: main course
cuisine: Southern Europe
time required: 20 minutes
author: Sara Heilman
nutrition:
  calories: 810 kcal
